title: What Will Microsoft Do If It Can't Buy Activision?
description:
Microsoft! Xbox! Activision! Bobby! We all wanna know what happens if Microsoft buys Activision, but what if they don’t? Do we care about that? Should we? I don’t know!

Join me as I take some guesses about what happens if the Microsoft Activision acquisition is no more. 

It might be interesting! Or maybe there’s a reason nobody is really talking about this.

Because it might not be interesting. I really don’t know.
